Thank you for using XFollow Chrome Extension. This Privacy Policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have concerning your data. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your personal information.

Information We Collect:

    Usage Data:
    We may collect data on how you interact with the extension, including but not limited to feature usage, preferences, and settings. This data helps us improve the functionality and user experience of the extension.

    Personal Information:
    The extension does not collect any personally identifiable information unless explicitly provided by the user for specific functionalities. We do not access, store, or process sensitive information.

How We Use Your Information:

    Improving User Experience:
    Collected data is used to analyze user interactions, identify patterns, and enhance the overall user experience of the extension.

    Communication:
    We may use your contact information to respond to your inquiries, provide customer support, or deliver important information about the extension.

    Aggregate Information:
    We may use aggregated, anonymized data for statistical analysis, research, and other business purposes.

Data Security:

We prioritize the security of your data and employ industry-standard measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

Third-Party Services:

The extension may utilize third-party services to facilitate certain functionalities. Please be aware that these services have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them for a comprehensive understanding.

Your Choices:

You have the right to review, update, or delete your personal information. If you have any concerns about your data, please contact us at [your contact email].

Updates to This Privacy Policy:

We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or for legal reasons. When we do, the revised date will be updated at the top of this page.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy or this policy, please contact us at [your contact email].

By using the [Your Company Name] Chrome Extension, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
